Author: Zukitten
Text: Oh gods, never has a truer word been spoken.  If I'm busy, I can just go straight through with nothing, but the moment I'm bored, that's it, I'm bingeing :(

Author: throwawayedfeelz
Text: THAT LAST LINE HIT HARD. I was just thinking earlier when I looked at the clock and it was only like 5pm that days seem so much longer when I don't fill it with eating???
